.SS Salt\-Master Customizations
.sp
To run salt\-master on OS X, the root user maxfiles limit must be increased:
.INDENT 0.0
.INDENT 3.5
.sp
.nf
.ft C
sudo launchctl limit maxfiles 4096 8192
.ft P
.fi
.UNINDENT
.UNINDENT
.sp
