.INDENT 0.0
.INDENT 3.5
.sp
.nf
.ft C
max_open_files: 8192
.ft P
.fi
.UNINDENT
.UNINDENT
.sp
Now the salt\-master should run without errors:
.INDENT 0.0
.INDENT 3.5
.sp
.nf
.ft C
sudo /usr/local/share/python/salt\-master \-\-log\-level=all
.ft P
.fi
