  job1:
    function: state.sls
    seconds: 3600
    args:
      \- httpd
    kwargs:
      test: True
    splay: 15
.ft P
.fi
.UNINDENT
.UNINDENT
.sp
This will schedule the command: state.sls httpd test=True every 3600 seconds
(every hour) splaying the time between 0 and 15 seconds
