.SS Proxmox
.sp
Using Salt with Proxmox requires a user, password and URL. These can be
obtained from your cloud provider. Both PAM and PVE users can be used.
.INDENT 0.0
.IP \(bu 2
Using the new configuration format:
.UNINDENT
.INDENT 0.0
.INDENT 3.5
.sp
.nf
