.INDENT 0.0
.INDENT 3.5
.sp
.nf
.ft C
svnfs_env_whitelist:
  \- base
  \- v1.*
  \- \(aqmybranch\ed+\(aq
.ft P
.fi
.UNINDENT
.UNINDENT
.SS \fBsvnfs_env_blacklist\fP
.sp
New in version 2014.7.0.

.sp
Default: \fB[]\fP
.sp
Used to restrict which environments are made available. Can speed up state runs
if your svnfs remotes contain many branches/tags. Full names, globs, and
