.TP
.B taps
Unofficial Github repos to use when updating and installing formulas.
.sp
CLI Example:
.INDENT 7.0
.INDENT 3.5
.sp
.nf
.ft C
salt \(aq*\(aq pkg.install <package name> tap=\(aq<tap>\(aq
