.INDENT 7.0
.IP \(bu 2
Local minion config (opts)
.IP \(bu 2
Minion\(aqs grains
.IP \(bu 2
Minion\(aqs pillar
.IP \(bu 2
Master config
.UNINDENT
.sp
CLI Example:
.INDENT 7.0
.INDENT 3.5
