The test works with 32 files with each file being 1Gb in size
The test consumes a lot of time. Be patient!
.sp
CLI Examples:
.INDENT 7.0
.INDENT 3.5
.sp
.nf
.ft C
salt \(aq*\(aq sysbench.fileio
.ft P
.fi
