to access. For these PPAs the username/password can be passed as an
HTTP Basic style username/password combination.
.INDENT 7.0
.INDENT 3.5
.sp
.nf
.ft C
logstash\-ppa:
  pkgrepo.managed:
    \- ppa: wolfnet/logstash
    \- ppa_auth: username:password
.ft P
.fi
.UNINDENT
