.SS Reminder
.sp
Just as with traditional pillars, external pillars must be refreshed in order for
minions to see any fresh data:
.INDENT 0.0
.INDENT 3.5
.sp
.nf
.ft C
salt \(aq*\(aq saltutil.refresh_pillar
.ft P
.fi
